                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.34521/15: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Lane</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-09-15T22:00:00-04:00"
                            >September 15, 1942—10 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>967. Your 1191 of September 12, 3 p.m. Your authority is contained in the last
                    paragraph of the Department’s telegram 959 of September 12.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
